OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776456351
OL,3,CCollege staff claim stagnant 'toxic'
OL,4,Cculture and 'emotional exhaustion'
OL,6,FStaff at a major post-16 college in
OL,7,FGuernsey allege a "high pressure ...
OL,8,Fand in places, toxic" workplace,
OL,9,Faccording to a damning report.
OL,11,FEmployees at The Guernsey Institute
OL,12,Fraised serious concerns through an
OL,13,Fexternal survey and focus groups about
OL,14,Fburnout, poor leadership and a lack of
OL,15,Ftrust in change.
OL,17,FThe provider offers a range of further
OL,18,Fand higher education courses through
OL,19,Fits University Centre, Guernsey
OL,20,FTraining Agency and the College of
OL,21,FFurther Education (FE).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
