OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776456351
OL,3,CCollege staff claim stagnant 'toxic'
OL,4,Cculture and 'emotional exhaustion'
OL,6,FThe culture and well-being review,
OL,7,Fcarried out in February, reveals "a
OL,8,Ffear of raising concerns", staff
OL,9,Ffacing passive aggression and
OL,10,Fallegations that some issues are
OL,11,Freported to management before any
OL,12,Fattempt by colleagues to address
OL,13,Fproblems directly between themselves.
OL,15,FThere are references to overbearing
OL,16,Famounts of bureaucracy, "burnout,
OL,17,Fchaos and reactivity," leaving some
OL,18,FCollege staff experiencing "emotional
OL,19,Fexhaustion" and "dread" as they
OL,20,Fstruggle to do their job and cover
OL,21,Fabsences.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776456351
OL,3,CCollege staff claim stagnant 'toxic'
OL,4,Cculture and 'emotional exhaustion'
OL,6,FCommon frustrations are raised about
OL,7,Fmanagers not being visible or
OL,8,Faccountable for the decisions they
OL,9,Fmake, with some staff believing
OL,10,Ffeedback is not acted upon and choices
OL,11,Fare made without consultation.
OL,13,FThe review acknowledges that there is
OL,14,F"a strong distrust as to whether
OL,15,Ffeedback from this process will
OL,16,Factually lead to change" and "specific
OL,17,Freferences to toxic behaviours
OL,18,Fremaining unaddressed".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776456351
OL,3,CCollege staff claim stagnant 'toxic'
OL,4,Cculture and 'emotional exhaustion'
OL,6,FIt adds: "Our interpretation was that
OL,7,Fthere are no clearly defined or
OL,8,Fconsistently enforced leadership or
OL,9,Fmanagement standards, and therefore no
OL,10,Fconsequence or accountability for poor
OL,11,Fbehaviour."
OL,13,FThe review paints a picture which is
OL,14,Fin stark contrast to The Institute's
OL,15,F"Together as One" motto.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776456351
OL,3,CCollege staff claim stagnant 'toxic'
OL,4,Cculture and 'emotional exhaustion'
OL,6,FHowever, it does state that many of
OL,7,Fthese sentiments are largely felt
OL,8,Fwithin the College of FE, rather than
OL,9,Fthe University Centre or Guernsey
OL,10,FTraining Agency, with focus groups for
OL,11,Fthose areas being more positive.
OL,13,FThe report also highlights that
OL,14,F"despite fatigue, people do genuinely
OL,15,Fwant things to change" and "staff
OL,16,Fremain deeply committed to students".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
