OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776456351
OL,3,CCollege staff claim stagnant 'toxic'
OL,4,Cculture and 'emotional exhaustion'
OL,6,FMoreover, most of those surveyed still
OL,7,Fsay they feel generally positive about
OL,8,Fgoing to work, with more than three-
OL,9,Fquarters stating they feel cared for
OL,10,Fand supported by their team.
OL,12,FThe review concludes by saying that
OL,13,F"in parts of the organisation,
OL,14,Fwellbeing is currently under strain,
OL,15,Fwith a risk of further deterioration
OL,16,Fif underlying pressures are not
OL,17,Faddressed".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
