OL,3,CCollege staff claim stagnant 'toxic'
OL,4,Cculture and 'emotional exhaustion'
OL,6,FIt encourages The Institute to view
OL,7,Fthis as an opportunity to make lasting
OL,8,Fchange and improve the experiences of
OL,9,Fits staff.
OL,11,FITV News has contacted The Guernsey
OL,12,FInstitute and the Committee for
OL,13,FEducation for their response.
